<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2521">أَبُو حَازِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2676">سَهْلٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا نُصَلِّي مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> الْجُمُعَةَ، ثُمَّ تَكُونُ الْقَائِلَةُ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>